    "Simultaneously, user-inputted text questions are embedded and converted into word vectors.",
    "The system connects these vectors to the vector database, performing a semantic search and ranking the relevance between vectors.",
    "The semantic search results in relevant context between questions and answers.",
    "The system retrieves pertinent answers based on user queries and sends them to the LLM (using the ChatGPT model).",
    "The final outcome involves the system receiving LLM-generated answers and delivering them to the user."
